## Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/og-model-assistant.git
cd og-model-assistant-pro
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py
```

## Features

- 🔍 Smart Search
- 💬 AI Chat
- 🎤 Voice Input
- 🖼️ Vision AI
- 💎 Free Tokens (auto-claim every 5h)
- 🌓 Dark/Light Theme

